{"tid":378390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「中共又避過一打劫」 印度同意撤軍 中印洞朗軍事對峙結束","createTime":"2017-08-28T12:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T19:17:49.000Z","uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d83f8439161fbfe04d0b20dc26e9a9db34b83057","tid":378390,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T12:43:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170828/57139080\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170828%2F57139080&d=mD2hx2PZ2ZJI7FJ23SHwSi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=a1ebbd58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170828%2F57139080&h=6b0c9926\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170828/57139080</a><br />\n<br />\n如果印度打入去, 中共就收皮<br />\n做乜撚野又撤軍, 又比中共過到關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過印度家陣國內爆發大暴動, 唔知有冇關係"},{"pid":"7c66906a596035320258b6f57a7744941b3d1ca3","tid":378390,"uid":13816,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T12:47:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d8b29f9e34721e3d0071784359c80145c99806c","tid":378390,"uid":65128,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T12:48:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f65fd8625814a85e7254051d3b4c5813260f5eab","tid":378390,"uid":53705,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T12:49:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戇鳩 印度咁撚勁就打撚左入去，佢依家擺到明鳩縮啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n印度一直霸住中國領土 一個月<br />\n中共連續發左20幾次開戰聲明, 但一槍都未開過<br />\n<br />\n印度佔盡優勢, 真係睇唔出點解印度要撤軍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n印度撤軍, 可能性只有一個<br />\n就係中共背後提供左一D 利益比印度, 印度拎到利益, 所以退兵"},{"pid":"dc9ca52095b805b4a1839b65979248001ccc089d","tid":378390,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T12:50:41.000Z","msg":"另外, 早係7月, 已經有大陸人講<br />\n<br />\n印度霸佔果座山, 9月會大雪, 到時雙方都要走, 無得留<br />\n<br />\n起初我以為D大陸人係吹水<br />\n<br />\n但家陣諗諗下, 可能係真<br />\n今日是8月28日, 差唔多9月, 印度就退兵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1592da14ac22efcabd80764e2ebc90da3ad4a7ed","tid":378390,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T12:52:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戇鳩 印度咁撚勁就打撚左入去，佢依家擺到明鳩縮啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係印度軍佔領緊塊地 唔係中國喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d5c8d2e58617a0b40c516e48ee2703d90008ee","tid":378390,"uid":135811,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T12:53:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>戇鳩 印度咁撚勁就打撚左入去，佢依家擺到明鳩縮啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n印度一直霸住中國領土 一個月<br />\n中共連續發左20幾次開戰聲明, 但一槍都未開過<br />\n<br />\n印度佔盡優勢, 真係睇唔出點解印度要撤軍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n印度撤軍, 可能性只有一個<br />\n就係中共背後提供左一D 利益比印度, 印度拎到利益, 所以退兵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n蝻仔淆就淆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />洗乜幫佢辯護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支仔都怯不愧係二流強國<br />\n<br />\n打得贏班蝻強姦犯兵圑神早入咗西藏姦淫擄掠啦"},{"pid":"a5d2fe0bffc72642c69c26382a18df2e47d9abe3","tid":378390,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T12:55:20.000Z","msg":"笑死<br />\n印度霸左地<br />\n再大家撤軍<br />\n印度就去番原本塊地<br />\n支那就要縮水<br />\n咁邊個輸啊？"},{"pid":"31e8e7559a755bd06910db6a4ba42e868da69030","tid":378390,"uid":65128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T12:59:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb7cc4b4795e184afb4ebbc010e3762a0ae6481b","tid":378390,"uid":135811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T13:02:36.000Z","msg":"真係唔明印度早支那成三十年發展社會經濟但到依家仲虧過支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />女人賤過雞，又有種姓分人等級(好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" cla